column1: # "unilib" remix - contains almost all packages which are original to unilib, and which typically do
#       not appear in other remixes. (A handful of original packages are listed, but commented out)
# For a list of packages providing all 118 chemical elements, use the "elements" package
# See the STANDARDS file for more information about what belongs in each category, and what does not
# packages from other mods, completing the periodic table
# N.B. all supporting packages are commented out, as this remix is not intended for gameplay
